reviewText: The continuation of the "Project Shadowchaser " series. All the cheesy action and ridiculo us dialog/punch lines that you can hope for. So stupid, it's great for B-Movie lovers.

nightsiege is terminator meets die hard. exciting from beginning to end. The other movie, Project Shadowchaser 3000 is terminator meet alien. Both movie are intense,graphic,and nailbiting to the very end.
